    "Aspect-based sentiment analysis (ABSA) is a significant area of research within the field of fine-grained sentiment analysis.",
    "One of the critical tasks in ABSA is aspect category opinion sentiment Quadruple Extraction (ACOSQE), which involves extracting four elements of information from text, including category, aspect, opinion, and sentiment polarity.",
    "ACOSQE has practical applications in business evaluation and public opinion analysis.",
    "It has recently become a popular research topic, with numerous scholars devoting attention to it.",
    "The process of ACOSQE is illustrated in Fig. 1."
